folder: Stagg Street & Graham Avenue, Brooklyn, NY
text:
175-177 Stagg Street (right), north side, east of Graham Ave., as seen across clearance at the S.E. corner. Also, shown are Nos. 218-226 Graham Ave., (left), east side, north of Stagg Street. Across the demolition at the right, appear buildings on the north side of Ten Eyck Street, between Humboldt Street and Bushwick Ave., beyond which is seen the steeple of St. Catherine's Hospital.

September 26, 1935.

P. L. Sperr.
